message.content: cs.CV, cs.Medical Imaging, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with semantic contour detection in medical imaging, specifically in placental ultrasound images. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and medical imaging (cs.Medical Imaging). The paper also proposes a new approach that incorporates global context modelling and multi-scale feature aggregation, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning and deep learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper uses a subject-level 10-fold nested cross-validation, which is a common technique in neural network training and evaluation (cs.NEURON).
